# rpcVersionMismatch

**Type Property**

The version of the remote procedure call (RPC) is incorrect.

## Declaration

```swift
static var rpcVersionMismatch: Errno { get }
```

## Discussion

The version of RPC on the remote peer isn’t compatible with the local version.

The corresponding C error is `ERPCMISMATCH`.

## RPC Errors

- **rpcProcedureUnavailable**: Bad procedure for program.
- **rpcProgramUnavailable**: The remote procedure call (RPC) program isn’t available.
- **rpcProgramVersionMismatch**: The version of the remote procedure call (RPC) program is incorrect.
- **rpcUnsuccessful**: The structure of the remote procedure call (RPC) is bad.
